### First, login to get token
POST http://localhost:54955/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Save the token from response, then use it below
### Replace YOUR_TOKEN with the actual token

### Get Cart (View current cart)
GET http://localhost:54955/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Add item to cart (productId=1, quantity=2)
POST http://localhost:54955/api/cart/add/1?quantity=2
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Add another item
POST http://localhost:54955/api/cart/add/2?quantity=1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Update item quantity (change product 1 to quantity 5)
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/cart/update/1?quantity=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Remove item from cart
DELETE http://localhost:54955/api/cart/remove/2
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Clear entire cart
DELETE http://localhost:54955/api/cart/clear
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN